\lim_{x \to \infty}{\sqrt{x^{200} +x^{100}+1}-x^{100}}
\sqrt{x^{200} + x^{100} + 1} - x^{100} = \dfrac{x^{100} + 1}{\sqrt{x^{200} + x^{100} + 1} + x^{100}} = \dfrac{1 + x^{-100}}{\sqrt{1 + x^{-100} + x^{-200}} + 1}
\frac{1}{2}
